        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Share a memory of a holiday. Where was it, who went, what happened?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>I remember me, the next year, I saw a beatiful girl. She speaks Italian and me French, we couldn't speak together but she didn't stop to watch to me, and me too ... I'm really tired because I know I could try something to kiss her but I didn't have the courage ... We I had to leave the aqualand, she comes and give me kiss on my cheek. I was really happy but I knew I'll never see her again. But I think to her occasionaly ! Her and her kiss ...</p>
            </div>
